text:
As you can see, today's outfit is amazing!
Look!

I've never worn this kind of outfit before,
so I did some research, but I think I overdid it...!

As a result of my wandering,
I ended up moving a bit slower than usual...

Hey, everyone, how was it?
Did it look elegant?

If you thought "it's kinda cool",
I'd be really happy!

(While still being Meguru-like,
moving with more ease than usual...)

(I'm sure it was tough with various timings being off,
but this is Meguru's potential...!)
